Castell Alun Football Club are a &lt;a href="association%20football"&gt;football&lt;/a&gt; club based in &lt;a href="Hope%2C%20Flintshire"&gt;Hope&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Flintshire"&gt;Flintshire&lt;/a&gt;. They currently play in the &lt;a href="North%20East%20Wales%20Football%20League"&gt;North East Wales Football League&lt;/a&gt; Premier Division. The home colours are Green &amp; Black shirts, black shorts and black socks &lt;a href="http%3A//www.faw.org.uk/competitions/clubs/144"&gt;Castell Alun Colts on Football Association of Wales&lt;/a&gt;
History.
The club joined the newly formed &lt;a href="North%20East%20Wales%20Football%20League"&gt;North East Wales Football League&lt;/a&gt; in 2020 as a Premier Division club.
